agent-session-manager (0.10.0) noble; urgency=medium

  * Multi-agent support: a provider framework now manages Cursor sessions
    alongside Claude Code. The sidebar lists both, each row badged with its
    agent icon; the New Session menu offers one entry per installed agent;
    resume, close, and fork route through each session's own agent.

